  "intro": "JS2IL implements the core get/set/has proxy traps plus deleteProperty, ownKeys, apply, construct, getPrototypeOf, setPrototypeOf, and revocable proxies. Proxy support is still incomplete because descriptor-heavy traps and full Proxy invariant enforcement are not modeled yet."
